name: TurboTax 2013 State Tax Form
summary: Learn about .TT2013STATE files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: TurboTax Deluxe, Premier, and Home & Business editions include a free state return. You can download the state version you need directly within TurboTax by clicking the Download button where the state refund amount is displayed. The TT2013STATE files that are downloaded will automatically be loaded by the program, meaning you do not have to open them manually.
